/>\n2) Brexit and economic recession<br />\nBaba Vanga saw the Brexit crisis in 2016 and foresee and huge economic crisis for European countries. Europe is set to face a very tough year.<br />\n<br />\n3) Assassination attempt on Vladimir Putin<br />\nAccording to the Nostradamus of the Balkans, Putin will be the victim of an assassination attempt. The attempt on his life will come from a member of his own security team.<br />\n<br />\n4) Donald Trump will get sick<br />\nAs for Donald Trump, he risks coming down with a mysterious illness. He&rsquo;ll suffer from the same illness as the American diplomats in Cuba. Nausea, tinnitus and hearing loss are in store.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/baba-vanga-predictions-what-s-ahead-for-2020/ar-BBXYET8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbaba-vanga-predictions-what-s-ahead-for-2020%2Far-BBXYET8&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0eb52451\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/baba-vanga-predictions-what-s-ahead-for-2020/ar-BBXYET8</a>"},{"pid":"c68e87dbaf9badfb05d664fb9ce88e29a19674bf","tid":2227641,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"龍婆呢？"},{"pid":"8fe9216f74977a2c2f5e526ef0fac9be0e5dbfb6","tid":2227641,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"財神在心 一生好運日日有福蔭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78465dc23e7753056e9eccf875d4c20388cafe6e","tid":2227641,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c212045eecab55a207a5656fc3d248882adf89e8","tid":2227641,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"留名bin 9佢屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特朗普染疫　堪輿大師李居明：10月10日需過大難關<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3YVRnB.png\" data-thumbnail-